data.description: Welcome home in the Holiday Hills subdivision! Located at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, it offers the perfect balance of privacy and convenience. Greet guests and enjoy serene afternoons on your covered front porch, also the perfect place to sip your morning coffee. 3 Bedrooms + Bonus Room/Office/Possible 4th Bedroom plus a full, partially finished basement; so much room to spread out and the potential for additional finished living space. 2 Updated Full Baths + 1 Half Bathroom. The formal living and dining rooms offer elegant spaces for gatherings and special occasions. The family room is complemented by a gas fireplace to keep you warm during winter nights. The fully applianced eat-in kitchen is open to the family room, creating a welcoming, open-concept space for meals and entertaining. Enjoy the tranquility of a large, private rear yard. This home boasts new in 2023 furnace, air conditioning, and water heater, plus newer carpeting and fresh paint throughout, ensuring a fresh, welcoming atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting home your own.
